Invocation Name: laundry checker
des: A skill designed to provide Illinois residence hall students with information on availability of washing and drying machines at all on-campus locations. Queries are in near real-time off of the 3rd party vendor API that hosts the laundry information.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
